      <Desc>COMMUNITY-BASED SELF-HELP EFFORTS: NEJA issued grants for community organizing and COVID-19 medical education, advocacy and benefit, and justice for low-income, often essential, workers and to aid self-help efforts expand their emergency and supplemental food, utility and water advocacy to aid communities in keeping healthy.</Desc>
